{"word":"Ἰουνιᾶς","slug":"Ἰουνιᾶς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Ἰουνιᾶς, ᾶ, ὁ</el></b> thus accented as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ masc.\">masc.</a>, <b>Junias,</b> in many editions of the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Gk.\">Gk.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> for the person mentioned in <b><a href='B:520 16:7'>Ro 16:7</a>,</b> but <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ms.\">ms.</a> evidence points to stronger probability for a woman as spelled in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ N\">N</a> 27, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ rev.\">rev.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ed.\">ed.</a>, 8th printing (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Ἰουνία\">Ἰουνία</a></el> 1). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἰουνία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἰοῦστος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}